{"tid":957292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屈穎妍：西環有鬼！","createTime":"2018-12-27T02:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T03:35:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ccad21a8c0de9ad0f5e1ece6c9541d229273c48","tid":957292,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"西環有鬼乎？<br />\n<br />\n　　唔係吖，自西港島線開通，西營盤多了個地鐵站，樓價立即攀升，食肆店舖生意也滔滔，何以社會上仍有人提起西環如見鬼，踏足西環更如闖鬼域，聞之色變？<br />\n<br />\n　　日前，中聯辦主任王志民向立法會議員邀約，請他們元宵節一起午宴。請柬未發、地點未定，一眾反對派議員已經腳仔軟，又在圍爐抽生死籤，看看哪個要做代表發言？哪個負責舉牌玩嘢？哪個擺姿態不出席冇份出鏡？<br />\n<br />\n　　毛孟靜說，若午宴在中聯辦舉行，她就肯定不會出席。<br />\n<br />\n　　邵家臻說，午宴地點非常關鍵，「若要入中聯辦，好難會考慮。」<br />\n<br />\n　　譚文豪說，若可談重啟政改、雙普選、內地維權問題，「吃茶餐廳大排檔都無所謂」。<br />\n<br />\n　　一句講晒，入中聯辦食飯？咪搞！<br />\n<br />\n　　到底他們怕甚麼？怕王主任會吃人？怕一進中聯辦就回不來？怕那張「走進中聯辦」的照片成為永遠？怕裏面餐廳食物有毒？怕進去會被洗腦？&hellip;&hellip;真的好想知道，到底他們怕甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n　　中聯辦其實已開放了幾次，好多市民都進去打過卡，作為立法會議員、民意代表，如果連中聯辦都未入過，或者不敢入，如何為民請命？如何當溝通橋樑？<br />\n<br />\n　　最好笑還是民主黨的林卓廷和尹兆堅，他們說：「呢啲表面公關嘢，食完飯咪再揼多你幾拳」、「砍你殺你同時，又突然同你飲茶食飯，覺得好奇怪、好有違和感，成件事好諷刺」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n　　明眼人都看到，回歸廿一年，西環人說一句話，都會被千夫所指，說你干預香港事務，這些年，到底砍人者誰？出拳者誰？香港市民，心中有數了。殺人者說我無辜、醉酒佬說我冇醉，就是這種人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/398/20181227/728513/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F398%2F20181227%2F728513%2F&d=i5rxKKHPmPy3CA6H%2Fw9zAtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f0933127\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F398%2F20181227%2F728513%2F&h=b68f0647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/398/20181227/728513/</a>"},{"pid":"5a3eefcfedc4af264e9ce744d4929a4b69ef5dd4","tid":957292,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"西營盤死城款喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21113737c369470f012f452ff6da8a2b4e4bae2","tid":957292,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:20:12.000Z","msg":"約食飯，咪去西環同金鐘中間lor"},{"pid":"d9a5629d34469e74f8a79d9cac226f906f0272df","tid":957292,"uid":81562,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"Do not make 文妓 famous<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774f78b5beedea8e1047a9a20bbb7ceff0284dec","tid":957292,"uid":190333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:23:45.000Z","msg":"第一段已經唔係事實啦<br />\n業主加哂租迫走D店搞到靜英英"},{"pid":"628fa8ab35804e9cf9c05a9f98d21f1def961900","tid":957292,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"屈文妓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04075e7583071f65278d0accf7361876f566abc6","tid":957292,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2BCRZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2BCRZm.jpg&h=09612e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9Ug7xH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9Ug7xH.jpg&h=0dee98ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乜撚野人黎"},{"pid":"c0642acafa9fa98aa942ce2e398449a54d4d2291","tid":957292,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:29:56.000Z","msg":"中式打飛機文章 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b8d2ce904d3dffac94b8962dd7f82c3223f498","tid":957292,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}